<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- wqt ạlsẖdẗ wwqt ạlḍyq .. mdyt ly ạ̹ydk yạ yswʿ
 fy ạlʿạlm mạlqytsẖ ṣdyq .. ysẖbʿny mn bʿd ạljwʿ
 (wḥdk tsẖbʿny wtrwyny .. mn ạ̉ʿẓm wạṭhr ynbwʿ)2
 mn ạ̉ʿẓm wạṭhr ynbwʿ
 1- wsṭ ậlạmy lqytk rby .. tḥmlny wtṭyb qlby
 ʿzytny fy ḥzny wkrby .. qwytny fy hmy wtʿby
 (myn gẖyrk kạn wạqf jnby .. ymsḥ mn ʿyny ạldmwʿ)2
 ymsḥ mn ʿyny ạldmwʿ
 2- ḥbk gẖạly mạ ạ̉ʿẓm ḥbk .. ḥbytny yạ yswʿ mn qlbk
 wqblt tṭhrny bdmk .. wậtẖạmy kẖbythạ fy jnbk
 (gẖmrtny ḥnyẗ qlbk .. bʿd mạ kạn ạ̉mly mqṭwʿ)2
 bʿd mạ kạn ạ̉mly mqṭwʿ</lyrics>
